                            <comment id="17881922" author="paulk" created="Mon, 16 Sep 2024 05:56:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Current status: hashing algorithm is now configurable thanks. Default is still md5. Plan is to test more on master and if further testing shows sha256 to be as fast as md5, swap the default on master (for Groovy 5).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If testing isn&apos;t finished before we make the next release, I&apos;ll clone the issue and split out that work.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
